## Error Handling Strategy

### Error Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Frontend UI
    participant Service as Frontend Service
    participant API as Backend API
    participant DB as Database
    
    UI->>Service: User action
    Service->>API: HTTP request
    
